    "description": "亲爱的中文玩家：<br><strong>本游戏尚未完全汉化。</strong>汉化工作目前正由我们的本地化志愿者团队负责推进，已基本完成界面文本（如物品介绍、百科词条、任务描述等）及教程关卡“荒原朝圣者”的正文翻译。后续完成的汉化内容将持续更新至游戏中。由于游戏文本量庞大，完全汉化可能需要较长时间，恳请大家耐心等待。如果您也希望为汉化工作贡献一份力量，欢迎前往Paratranz在线翻译平台，搜索“Vagrus”项目申请加入。感谢大家对本游戏的关注与支持！<br><br>《瓦格鲁斯》是一款获奖众多的角色扮演游戏，以叙事为中心，拥有开放世界探索和显著的策略元素。玩家将扮演一位“瓦格鲁斯”——即“行督”（旅行团体的领袖），带领自己的队伍在这片黑暗而诡谲的幻想世界中投身形形色色的冒险，并奋力谋求生存。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/0d5fa2c8b476afe74b577c53f5757604.avif?t=1771238005\" width=611 height=78 /></span><br>风格迥异的地点、鱼龙混杂的派系势力、丰富多彩的人物角色……广袤无垠的国度等待着您的探索。为了惩罚帝国所犯下的罪孽，上古诸神在千年前降下神罚，摧毁了整个国度。如今，这片大陆业已成为荒原；纵使经历了漫长的重建，大陆上依然充斥着神秘的异象、游荡着扭曲的怪物，更有成群结队、肆意横行的不死生物。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/2200b363bb5f3c3bdb418f61d95cc3c5.poster.avif?t=1771238005\" width=612 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/2200b363bb5f3c3bdb418f61d95cc3c5.webm?t=1771238005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/2200b363bb5f3c3bdb418f61d95cc3c5.mp4?t=1771238005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/f2bcacd6e75cea63cfec82ff3e70f63e.webp?t=1771238005\" width=611 height=30 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/39c6062de7a3ae5b7592d4f1d885ff52.avif?t=1771238005\" width=611 height=78 /></span><br>事件、任务和一个个故事组成了游戏叙事的主体部分。您在事件中做出的抉择，往往会对同伴及周遭的世界产生深远影响。选择您的起始背景，以商人、雇佣兵或探险家的身份踏入荒原；为各大派系效力，打听传闻并追寻机遇；积攒巨额财富、建立赫赫威名，或窥探隐秘学识。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/e10bea8fcbd8087075ca016387e95562.poster.avif?t=1771238005\" width=612 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/e10bea8fcbd8087075ca016387e95562.webm?t=1771238005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/e10bea8fcbd8087075ca016387e95562.mp4?t=1771238005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/f2bcacd6e75cea63cfec82ff3e70f63e.webp?t=1771238005\" width=611 height=30 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/953750578db204c29a3c8c09fa32dbe3.avif?t=1771238005\" width=611 height=78 /></span><br>指挥您的同伴们，在回合制策略战斗中与各类强敌抗衡；挡住前路的既可能是类人生物，也可能是妖魔鬼怪。利用海量角色技能，以及自己的领袖能力来赢得胜利。在这些困难的挑战中，站位与使用技能的策略举足轻重。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/7b4c209c696caa0d27a226f69cb50abe.poster.avif?t=1771238005\" width=612 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/7b4c209c696caa0d27a226f69cb50abe.webm?t=1771238005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/7b4c209c696caa0d27a226f69cb50abe.mp4?t=1771238005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/f2bcacd6e75cea63cfec82ff3e70f63e.webp?t=1771238005\" width=611 height=30 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/2a5aedb4cffea7a0acdc5740b77d32a0.avif?t=1771238005\" width=611 height=79 /></span><br>您的每段旅途都必须精打细算、步步为营；否则一着不慎，便会满盘皆输。为了生存，您需要严格管理物资补给、队伍士气以及队员精力。您将在荒原上贩运货物，或从他人手中巧取豪夺。只有运营得当，才能让这个由劳工、战士、斥候与奴隶组成的队伍保持运转。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/4a74f207bed9bda369dee172f9d508ae.poster.avif?t=1771238005\" width=612 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/4a74f207bed9bda369dee172f9d508ae.webm?t=1771238005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/4a74f207bed9bda369dee172f9d508ae.mp4?t=1771238005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/f2bcacd6e75cea63cfec82ff3e70f63e.webp?t=1771238005\" width=611 height=30 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/bbbd4c30d528b2a8c4f725f23dfe7538.avif?t=1771238005\" width=611 height=79 /></span><br>各式各样的同伴将为您效力，担任不同的副官角色，例如侦察队长、守卫队长、护卫法师或驯兽总管。每个同伴都有其独特的战斗技能、背景故事与个人任务；当你完成这些个人任务时，同伴便能进一步升级。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/70ecd1f75aee5dada4eb3fdfaec275d9.poster.avif?t=1771238005\" width=612 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/70ecd1f75aee5dada4eb3fdfaec275d9.webm?t=1771238005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/70ecd1f75aee5dada4eb3fdfaec275d9.mp4?t=1771238005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/f2bcacd6e75cea63cfec82ff3e70f63e.webp?t=1771238005\" width=611 height=30 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/c9d1965bd28889ae08cb3f9cfada27bb.avif?t=1771238005\" width=611 height=84 /></span><br>众多强大的派系通过商业影响、血腥杀戮与阴谋诡计一手缔造了如今的万壑之地，而你有机会与这些派系结盟。上到生意兴隆的商贸集团，下至犯罪帮会与宗教组织，这些团体会为他们忠实的追随者提供优渥的奖励与恩惠。但请务必小心：与一些派系交好，往往意味着与另一些派系为敌。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/63ff0fc8c9ac934f85f8b687b5e57663.poster.avif?t=1771238005\" width=612 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/63ff0fc8c9ac934f85f8b687b5e57663.webm?t=1771238005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/909660/extras/63ff0fc8c9ac934f85f8b687b5e57663.mp4?t=1771238005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
